'''''N''-氯哌啶'''是[[哌啶|哌啶]]氮上的氢被[[氯|氯]]取代的产物，化学式为C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>10</sub>NCl。
==制备==
[[哌啶乙酸盐|哌啶乙酸盐]]和[[次氯酸钙|次氯酸钙]]在0℃的水溶液中反应，得到''N''-氯哌啶。<ref>{{OrgSynth | author = George P. Claxton, Lloyd Allen, and J. Martin Grisar | title = 2,3,4,5-Tetrahydropyridine trimer| collvol = 6 | collvolpages = 968 | year = 1988 | prep = CV6P0968}}</ref>

